title: Cindy Crawford introduced her children Presely and Kaia Gerber as Omega's newest ambassadors
description:
(29 Sep 2017) CINDY CRAWFORD INTRODUCES HER CHILDREN AS THE NEWEST AMBASSADORS FOR LUXURY WATCHMAKER OMEGA
Cindy Crawford introduced her children Presley and Kaia Gerber as OMEGA's newest ambassadors at the opening of the luxury brand's "Her Time" exhibition in Paris on Friday (29 Sept. 2017).  
The supermodel has been Omega's most emblematic ambassador and now her children are following in her footsteps.  
Sixteen year-old Kaia Jordan Gerber, who recently made her catwalk debut and has a striking resemblance with her mother, posed confidently with her 18-year old brother Presley in front of photographers. 
The family was joined by Omega CEO Raynald Aeschlimann on the red carpet. 
The luxury watchmaker has been working with Crawford for over 20 years.
